Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一堆衣服都沒辦法洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.82,0:01:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣象報告說下午會暫停一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的停雨那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.66,0:01:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能早點轉為秋天 那就更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.27,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳喜歡秋天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.44,0:01:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋高氣爽的天氣給人好舒服的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過春天也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像妳的風格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希喜歡秋天嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡 很涼爽舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒所謂的喜不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.80,0:02:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽潑春說這傢伙一碰到雨天就會變得渾身無力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪他最近心情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你要睡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是這樣 真沒路用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.38,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比你賴床…好多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.82,0:02:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的不舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 真是討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的很不舒服就不要勉強自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.00,0:02:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 如果撐傘會很累的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我幫你撐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.74,0:02:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.91,0:02:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能讓女人幫我撐傘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不這樣吧 我知道你可能不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.02,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但可以變身為貓讓我抱你回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更糟的提議啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都叫妳別這麼雞婆了 別再惹我生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.73,0:03:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒什麼好道歉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不我今晚煮些增加精力的菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別管我就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的體質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 一到家雨就停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多希望雨一直下 才能樂得耳根清淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你說什麼了 臭老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾…我好像聽到"鏗鏘"一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關了也沒用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 阿夾你怎麼了 門怎麼打不開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.08,0:04:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 可能一輩子都打不開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.55,0:04:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事快說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然沒有就別來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 人家想見你 所以來見你也不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想見妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好過分 竟然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧人家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧人家這麼愛你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我厭惡妳的原因之一 妳怎麼還不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂羅 那個借妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們去約個會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 那就拜託他們兩人買晚餐的材料啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我不要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就去約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐策略成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們獨處一下 樂羅才能冷靜些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而家裡也不會遭殃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.21,0:05:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過大門的修繕費又得跟本家申請了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 跟本家申請嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 總之這個家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有草摩本家的援助才能維持啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在這裡寄人籬下一年多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對於這個家的事還有內情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍有許多不瞭解之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去洗衣服好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雨很快就會再下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得有這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看小透就跟由希去約個會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不介意去秘密基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說想瞭解這裡或許有點癡人說夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.70,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是很想瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴 慢慢來也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需能慢慢瞭解大家就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望自己能坦然接受現有的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.23,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很擔心自從那時候起到底變成怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.57,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子讓我看到那樣的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看也差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.48,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓那隻蠢貓現出原形了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.36,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.43,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩看到後會露出什麼樣的表情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會忍不住奪門而出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候 由希肯定會失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜單裡也有阿夾最愛吃的鱈魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透她還不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.51,0:07:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算一直瞞著她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆 這件事跟妳無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.09,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在公共場所斥責女孩子 真是最差勁的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾真是 真是太丟臉了 我們快去那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會這麼在意我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常人一定會避開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會和我保持距離吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾一定不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕你聽了會哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去結帳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像又快要下雨了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不肯說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手牽手回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打死都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前常常手牽手的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是3.4歲大的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 好無情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳牽手就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只牽一下子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.61,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.25,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常一般人一定會避開或和我保持距離吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.42,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾你真的不記得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你主動的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂羅姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主動對我伸出援手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主動前來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時阿夾的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.69,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂羅姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又開始下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道阿夾跟樂羅他們還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他暈倒了樂羅也一定會揹他回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽這麼久了也牽夠本了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明知我最討厭人家死纏著我不放啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖知道 但還是覺得掃興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.69,0:11:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.88,0:11:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你看起來挺不錯的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你安然無恙我就安心了 籍真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.10,0:12:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳也是 很高興知道你小說寫得挺順暢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是阿夾的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父 久違了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久疏問候 師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 樂羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希則是長高了不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.82,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 這位是草摩籍真 是阿夾的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是由希、樂羅和波鳥的武術師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.93,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫妳小透嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 初次見面 我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 就是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了不少妳的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於十二生肖的事妳也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別老躲在一旁啊 也過來跟師父打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也打從去年在山中至今都沒見過師父吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟師父重逢 難道你不開心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾的房間在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 我進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看了不少書嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.82,0:13:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我的態度很差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在由希面前不服輸的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.87,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父 歡迎你回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.87,0:13:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說師父並非十二生肖之一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.68,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不過算是跟本家很親的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.88,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為附身在阿夾身上的貓就是師父的祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.39,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以最瞭解阿夾立場的可能就是師父吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.03,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且師父好像非常珍惜阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處處小心翼翼好怕他受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有如親生父親般疼他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有如親生父親般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說師父修行之旅也告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能再擱著道場不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 我也能回道場囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我們離別時做好的約定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來後 再一起生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們暫時得分開一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你想違背約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.61,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得這個環境最適合你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就住在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.78,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是巧合或是必然 住在這裡對你是最…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是討厭這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像溫水般要死不活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會難受得讓自己吃不消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的吧 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一點也不討厭這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父今晚會住這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去請問師父要睡哪裡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去問他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:16:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可能會因取下那個而驚動了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡先跟你道個歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何突然做出這樣的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天看到那孩子的臉後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得她的話應該能打開那孩子的心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那女孩也應該會接納他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.25,0:16:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我深覺這是個看清一切的最佳時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.06,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把一切都交託給那女孩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,籍真 連你也這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我也沒把握會成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定阿夾這次真的會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.38,0:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連你都恨 也不再對你露出笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都想賭這萬分之一的機會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能做成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父對這個最沒轍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 簡單說我也是得繼續修業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 我還是想賭賭看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一切賭在她身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小透而言 這將是多殘酷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.21,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚能耽誤妳一點時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想談什麼可以在裡面談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.87,0:18:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我最怕這種天氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.21,0:18:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我祖父也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.78,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一到雨天身體狀況就很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了被貓附身這個原因之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上原本有毛的動物就討厭雨的本性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.49,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多該接納這個事實 否則會裹足不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就接納了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.99,0:19:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打一出生就被貓附身 從那一刻起就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.89,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這一切也都因為那隻臭老鼠的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也知道那傢伙就是元凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.81,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今後打算繼續這麼活下去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.78,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝聾作啞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著恨由希的心隱瞞所有的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能用這樣的方式來捍衛自己嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.00,0:20:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…就這麼孤零零的死去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我祖父那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其實不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是討厭這裡而是想逃避這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為溫水這股溫暖的情意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是可以治癒受傷的心靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真實的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想被知道真正的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕被知道後會失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一心企圖想逃避這曖昧的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 那我就拉住那想溜走的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看是會失去還是會得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起來驗收成果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.56,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.90,0:21:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來看看你的人生是不是真的完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.95,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我愛你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用給別人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不要去看別人 我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看！

